➜Nantong Blue Calico training courses started
http://www.sohu.com/a/420363926_162758	36490
<p><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200923/d01f5fdf65954f199688956d5232051a.jpeg" /></p>
<p>On Spet 21, 2020 the opening ceremony of Nantong Blue Calico training courses was held at Nantong University, east China's Jiangsu Province. The training courses are part of the China intagible cultural heritage training programme supported by the Ministry of Culture and Tourism, the Ministry of Education and the Ministry of Human Resources and Social Security. The 30 trainees who will participate in the one-month free training are mainly inheritors of printing and dyeing and workshop designers from Yunnan, Guizhou, Gansu and Shandong. (Xu Congjun/Guangming Picture)</p>
